ofc4j.model
Class Chart

java.lang.Object
  ofc4j.model.Chart
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Chart
extends Object
implements Serializable

This is the most important class in the Java OFC library. Start here, configuring the title, axes, legends, labels, and draw-able elements in your chart. Coerce the object to a String with the toString() method to get the chart data back out.
